ZH: 我们三个人都同样疯狂地喜欢她，独独她只对他有感觉。
EN: The three of us all love her madly, but she has feelings only for him.

ZH: 在这个大街上，独独这家咖啡店一直开放到午夜。
EN: On this street, only this café remains open until midnight.

ZH: 他有很多钱，但独独没有幸福感。
EN: He has a lot of money, but he lacks happiness.

ZH: 这里有很多种冰淇淋口味，但我独独喜欢巧克力的。
EN: There are many flavors of ice cream here, but I only like chocolate.

ZH: 他们全都是天才，独独她是个普通人。
EN: They are all geniuses, except for her who is an ordinary person.

ZH: 这家餐厅的菜都很好吃，独独它的招牌菜最受欢迎。
EN: The dishes in this restaurant are all delicious, but the signature dish is especially popular.

ZH: 这个小镇的房价一直在上涨，独独这个地区的价格保持稳定。
EN: The housing prices in this town have been rising, but the prices in this area remain stable.

ZH: 在这个大家庭中，兄弟姐妹都结婚生子了，独独他还单身。
EN: In this big family, all the siblings are married and have children, except for him who is still single.

ZH: 这段视频有很多有趣的瞬间，独独最后一幕最引人注目。
EN: This video has many interesting moments, but the last scene is the most eye-catching.

ZH: 这个团队每个人都做得很好，独独她的贡献最大。
EN: Everyone in this team is doing great, but her contribution is the greatest.

ZH: 这个城市有很多购物中心，独独这个是最大的。
EN: This city has many shopping malls, but this one is the biggest.

ZH: 这个故事里有许多可怕的怪物，独独最可怕的是那只巨大的龙。
EN: This story has many scary monsters, but the scariest one is the giant dragon.

ZH: 这次考试全班同学都得了A，独独他得了B。
EN: Everyone in the class got an A on the test, except for him who got a B.

ZH: 这个班级里的学生都很有礼貌，独独他总是有点粗鲁。
EN: The students in this class are all very polite, except for him who is always a bit rude.

ZH: 这个旅行团的人都是老朋友，独独他是新加入的。
EN: Everyone in this tour group is an old friend, except for him who just joined.

ZH: 这个国家严禁私人购买和拥有武器，独独警察和军队可以携带。
EN: This country strictly prohibits private purchase and possession of weapons, except for the police and military who are allowed to carry them.

ZH: 这个公园里有很多动物标本，独独这只恐龙骨架最引人注目。
EN: This park has many animal specimens, but the dinosaur skeleton is the most striking.

ZH: 这个音乐会有各种类型的音乐，独独爵士乐最受欢迎。
EN: This concert has various types of music, but jazz is the most popular.

ZH: 这个公司的员工都非常敬业，独独他总是拖延完成任务。
EN: The employees in this company are all very dedicated, except for him who always procrastinates tasks.

ZH: 这个房子有三个卧室，独独主卧带有独立浴室。
EN: This house has three bedrooms, but only the master bedroom has an en-suite bathroom.
